2.0.  CHANGED FEATURES
      
      CR20019914
      Deprecate RoleMapper_1_0 and remove dependency to openMDX/Security.
            
      CR10010109
      The method PortalExtension_1_0.isEnabled() was renamed to the more general
      method hasPermission(). The new signature allows to control show- and edit-
      permissions for GUI elements such as fields, field groups, operations and
      references.
            
